Class TupleDijkstra

java.lang.Object
processing.TupleDijkstra
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Comparable<TupleDijkstra>
public class TupleDijkstra
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<TupleDijkstra>
Encapsulates an intersection with its current distance to the starting point in a Dijkstra run. Used in a priority queue.

    Nested Classes 
    Modifier and Type Class Description
    (package private) static class  TupleDijkstra.Color
    Represents the different possible colors of a point in a Dijkstra run : - white if it has not been visited yet - gray if it has been visited but its predecessor has not been established yet - black if its predecessor has been established
